paragraphs.text:
%spark2

import org.apache.spark.mllib.linalg.Vectors 
import org.apache.spark.ml.feature.VectorAssembler

val ornlShortDF = df_ornlData.selectExpr("cast(rh_mean as double) rh_mean", 
                                           "cast(tbrg_precip_total as double) tbrg_precip_total",
                                           "cast(temp_mean as double) temp_mean"
                                          )
//Assemble the Feature Vector from extacted features values
val assembler = new VectorAssembler().setInputCols(Array("rh_mean","tbrg_precip_total","temp_mean")).setOutputCol("features")

//Create Feature Vector
val FeatureVector = assembler.transform(ornlShortDF)

//Display results
FeatureVector.take(10)
